NUMBER 2676
NAME Temple, Solarium
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
A polished marble floor and walls sparkle beautifully with the combined
brilliance of the gold and silver veins that flow aesthetically through
them. The threads of gold straighten along the western wall, rising up
like the rays of the sun to a small alcove which contains a statue, while
the silver threads do the same on the eastern wall. Forming the entire
ceiling of the circular chamber is a bowl-shaped piece of glass, through
which the sunlight, or moonlight, enters to bathe the entire chamber with
a beautiful glow. Directly in the center of the room is a large oak table
with numerous chairs placed around it and a ways beyond it is a majestic
marble desk, flowing seamlessly from the same piece used to craft the floor.
A crystal window in the far wall looks out over the beautiful sunken garden
in the center of the temple. A gold-flecked stairway descends into the temple
main.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1226 ADJ1=312 VAL2=1190
EXTEND 0 flecked with gold
ITEM 1 91 ADJ1=178
ITEM 2 201 ADJ1=312
ITEM 3 86
ITEM 4 1909
ITEM 5 346 ADJ1=468
ITEM 6 346 ADJ1=292
ITEM 7 249
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Set into the polished oak surface of the table are beautiful gold and
silver representations of the sun and moon.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
The front of the desk has been etched with alternating gold and silver
lettering that spells out:
      "In the light of our Lord, we become strong."
      "In the light of his Sister, we become cleansed."
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 5
The golden statue has been carved to portray Rorin standing amidst his fallen
enemies, his sword held tightly clenched in his hands and his face set
sternly to portray his determination against the forces of darkness.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 6
The silver statue has been beautifully carved to represent Elorna, gently
bathing a kneeling worshipper with the silvery light of her power, cleansing
her follower and healing his body and soul.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY
  IFVAR TIM => 7
   IFVAR TIM =< 12
     ECHO PLAYER Brilliant shafts of golden light beam through the open skylight, dancing off the brass and crystal to produce a dazzling display of rainbows. For the moment it takes for your eyes to adjust to the blinding sunlight, you see Rorin standing before you in the glare, perhaps just an image in the sun.
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
    IFVAR TIM => 19
     IFVAR TIM =< 23
       ECHO PLAYER Gentle starlight bathes the room throgh the open skylight, casting silver upon all it touches. The glints of metal and crystal in the room take on the appearance of hundred of stars before you. For the moment it takes your eyes to adjust to the soft starlight, you swear you saw an image of Elorna, Rorin's sister, standing beside you.
     ENDIF
    ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY I_seek_solace,_Elorna'cha.
  IFVAR ORG = 11
    ECHO PLAYER Silvery points of light stream from the skylight above, as they envelop you, you feel yourself drawn across great distances...
    ECHO OTHERS Silvery points of light stream from the skylight above enveloping %N and making %i fade from view...
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
    MOVEGROUP 2531
    AFFECT 2351
    ECHO PLAYER As your vision clears, you find yourself standing in a small clearing
    ECHO OTHERS %P arrives, enveloped in silvery points of light.
    AFFECT 2676
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB LOOK 4
  CLEARVERB
    IFVAR DAY = 1
      ECHO PLAYER The golden rays of the sun stream down through the beautiful skylight and flicker across the veins of gold throughout the chamber. As if reaching towards the sun the golden veins shimmer and flow towards each other, melding together to form a dazzling image of Rorin.
      ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER Reaching down from the night sky, gentle moonbeams caress the floor drawing forth the silvery veins that run throughout the marble. As if reaching towards the beauty of the moon the silvery veins rise up and join above the table to form the image of Rorin's sister, Elorna.
    ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 7
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You gaze out the window...
  ECHO OTHERS %N gazes out the window...
  SHOWROOM 33
ENDIF
