NUMBER 1191
NAME Temple of Rorin
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is a spacious area where the priests of the Temple of Rorin engage in the
tutelage of acolytes and adepts. The priests invite all to join in Rorin's
light, and demonstrate a working knowledge of nearly every skill imaginable.
The room is flanked by long stained wooden bookracks, and is filled with
tables, mats and workbenches decorated with a vast array of tools and
equipment. A rack of wooden weaponry sits in the corner for practice by
initiates.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 1190
ORGDEF 11 INVITE temple 1191 Temple_of_Rorin
IFENTRY -1
  ECHO ALL A wizened priestess totters to her feet and casts a spell.
  SPELL 250 100
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The elderly woman creaks back into her chair.
ENDIF
