NUMBER 1192
NAME Outer Temple, temple proper
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A rich crimson carpet splits the rows of carved stone pews and leads up to a
shimmering altar formed of a golden hued crystal. The walls are decorated with
rich red tapestries trimmed with white and gold. The ceiling stretches up to a
stained glass dome mounted by a golden spire which points to the heavens. A
gleaming alzyron statue of Rorin stands watch over the Temple from behind the
sparkling altar. The light shines through the stained glass ceiling onto the
altar and statue, surrounding them in a nimbus of golden flame. An arch at the
back of the room is flanked by Rorinite Centurions.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 1190
ITEM 0 60
ITEM 1 401 ADJ1=468 ADJ2=5
EXTEND 1 of Rorin
ITEM 2 236
ITEM 3 250
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Made of pure alzyron and imbued with a deep golden hue by the arcane might
of the gods this magnificent representation of Rorin stands proudly at
watch over his followers. Armed with a gigantic greatsword that has
flickering flames along its edge, the statue seems almost life-like, as if
part of Rorin himself resides within the alzyron interior.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB PRAY -1
  ECHO PLAYER The statue shimmers brilliantly and you feel the power of Rorin wash through your body.
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
The altar is carved from a huge piece of clear crystal, and topped by a white
marble slab trimmed in gold. A symbol of the Sun has been set into the front,
the central orb formed of platinum, with gold and silver rays shining outwards.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
There are eight tapestries depicting the faithful of Rorin engaged in their
duties; some are shown kneeling in prayer, some gather crops and tend herds,
while others are shown engaging dark forces in combat, wielding swords of
living flame.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;[Look Centurions: The finest of Rorins warriors, these Centurions stand guard
