NUMBER 1193
NAME Inner Temple, Mosaic
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Your senses reel as the power of Rorin infuses every part of your soul and
mind. Streaks of golden light dance from a beautiful mosaic set into the
center of the floor, flowing forth to submerge the room in their dazzling
brilliance. Outlined in the combined glow of the light are seven pedestals,
each with a beautiful crystal case set atop them, carefully arranged along
the floor of the chamber to represent the rays of the sun. A wide stairway
leads back up to the outer temple while a passage continues to the north.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 1194
ITEM 0 81 VAL2=1192
ITEM 1 547 ADJ1=37
EXTEND 1 of the sun
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Seven golden beams of light, forming the images of swords extend from
a central orb, shaped like the sun. Pulsating beams of light flow from
the tips of the sword and streak towards the seven pedestals
arranged carefully around the chamber.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ORG = 11
   ECHO PLAYER You feel yourself subsumed in the glory of Rorin, recharged by his power and strengthened in your resolve as his words of grandeur fill your spirit!
   ECHO OTHERS %N is covered with golden and silvery lights, %h face becoming beatific.
  ENDIF
   IFVAR ORG ! 11
     ECHO PLAYER You feel yourself covered in warmth, your senses reeling for a moment.
     ECHO OTHERS %N smiles beautifully as %s is covered in gold and silver light for a moment.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
