NUMBER 1194
NAME Inner Temple, Junction
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tiled walls of the hallway reflect the light of the small oil lamps that
line the hall. Passages continues to the west and south, and a stairway leads
down. On the eastern wall, a giant symbol of a golden orb surrounded by eight
fiery rays of light, seems to radiate head and light.
*DESCRIPTION_END
