NUMBER 35
NAME Under Temple, forge
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
ASTRAL
FORGE
*DESCRIPTION_START
At the heart of this circular chamber stands a forge of awe-inspiring
beauty. Made of pure gold, shot through with swirling streaks of alzyron
and elkyri, it stands as a timeless monument to the glory of Rorin and
those who craft in his name. Surrounding the majestic paean to the
smith's craft are the other tools of the trade, a large bellows, firepit,
mirmach barrel and a rack for holding tools.
*DESCRIPTION_END
